{"tid":1994131,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★負資產住宅按揭貸款宗數按季飆升2倍","createTime":"2020-04-29T09:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T10:58:42.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5ad569331052c5180cd933104e6097ef24b86f","tid":1994131,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T09:05:38.000Z","msg":"香港金融管理局公布，截至第一季末，負資產住宅按揭貸款宗數按季飆升2倍，至384宗。相關個案涉及銀行職員的住屋按揭貸款或按揭保險計劃的貸款，而這類貸款的按揭成數一般較高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200429/bkn-20200429164335320-0429_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200429%2Fbkn-20200429164335320-0429_00842_001.html&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=051cbb8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200429/bkn-20200429164335320-0429_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d5d425a2f7cef2d9bfa80131adde69540fdea061","tid":1994131,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T09:05:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3668e525a52b32e1a1c22d344a1d0b745de3ecc1","tid":1994131,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T09:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20160430/photo/0430-00176-002b1.jpg?t=1588151205425\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160430%2Fphoto%2F0430-00176-002b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1588151205425&h=24e2d900&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81e373270544f63aa8638b40872c5d30bdae0103","tid":1994131,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB